,"primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"마사순","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"马思纯，演员，毕业于中国传媒大学。妈妈蒋雯娟是演员蒋雯丽的大姐兼经纪人。\n\n1995年，7岁的马思纯参演了电影《三个人的冬天》；2000年，13岁时饰演《大宅门》少年白玉婷；2007年，因担任饶雪漫小说《甜酸》的书模而为人所知。2008年主演电视剧《爸爸，我怀了你的孩子》，由此进入演艺圈。同年与檀健次、莫文蔚、蒋雯丽共同出演了电影《秘岸》，2009年出演蒋雯丽执导的剧情片《我们天上见》。","name":"马思纯","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"馬思純，1988年出生於安徽蚌埠，畢業於中國傳媒大學，7歲參演過電影《三個人的冬天》，13歲飾演過《大宅門》少年白玉婷，於2008年主演電視劇《戀人》，由此開始進入演藝圈。","name":"馬思純","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mã Tư Thuần","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"馬思純，演員，畢業於中國傳媒大學。媽媽蔣雯娟是演員蔣雯麗的大姐兼經紀人。\n\n1995 年，7 歲的馬思純參演了電影《三個人的冬天》；2000 年，13 歲時飾演《大宅門》少年白玉婷；2007 年，因擔任饒雪漫小説《甜酸》的書模而為人所知。2008 年主演電視劇《爸爸，我懷了你的孩子》，由此進入演藝圈。同年與檀健次、莫文蔚、蔣雯麗共同出演了電影《秘岸》，2009 年出演蔣雯麗執導的劇情片《我們天上見》。","name":"馬思純","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"マー・スーチュン","primary":false}}]}},"person_41883_translations":{"at":1773513010555,"data":{"id":41883,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Maximillion Drake Thieriot (born October 14, 1988) is an American actor. He began his career with roles in many family films including \"Catch That Kid\" with Kristen Stewart, \"The Pacifier\" with Vin Diesel and \"Nancy Drew\" with Emma Roberts. In 2009, he co-starred in the erotic thriller \"Chloe\" alongside Julianne Moore, Liam Neeson, and Amanda Seyfried. In 2012, he starred in the horror film \"House at the End of the Street\" alongside Jennifer Lawrence. He currently plays Dylan Massett in A&E's drama thriller series \"Bates Motel\".","name":"Max Thieriot","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HU","iso_639_1":"hu","name":"Magyar","english_name":"Hungarian","data":{"biography":"Maximillion Drake \"Max\" Thieriot amerikai színész, legismertebb szerepe Dylan Massett a Bates Motel – Psycho a kezdetektől című televíziós sorozatban.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Maximillion „Max“ Drake Thieriot (* 14. Oktober 1988 in Los Altos Hills, Kalifornien) ist ein US-amerikanischer Schauspieler.\n\nEntdeckt wurde Thieriot in einer Improvisations-Klasse. Er modelte für GAP und trat auch in zwei Kurzfilmen auf, bevor er 2004 für den Film Mission: Possible – Diese Kids sind nicht zu fassen! gecastet wurde. Es folgten weitere Filme, unter anderem 2005 der Film Der Babynator sowie 2007 die Filme The Astronaut Farmer und Nancy Drew, Girl Detective. Im Jahr 2008 verkörperte er in dem Film Jumper eine jüngere Version der zentralen Hauptrolle, welche von Hayden Christensen gespielt wurde. Im Juni 2008 kam die Komödie Kit Kittredge: An American Girl mit Abigail Breslin in der Titelrolle in die Kinos.\n\nIm Jahr 2009 übernahm er Hauptrollen in Atom Egoyans Chloe und in Wes Cravens Horrorfilm My Soul to Take. In Mark Tonderais Psychothriller House at the End of the Street, der am 21. September 2012 in den US-amerikanischen Kinos startete, ist Thieriot an der Seite von Jennifer Lawrence zu sehen. Von 2013 bis 2017 war er in der Fernsehserie Bates Motel neben Vera Farmiga und Freddie Highmore zu sehen.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"（Maximillion Drake Thieriot，1988年10月14日-），美国演员。他的职业生涯始于许多家庭电影，包括与克里斯汀·斯图尔特合作的《抓住那个孩子》、与范·迪塞尔合作的《奶嘴》和与艾玛·罗伯茨合作的《南希·德鲁》。2009年，他与朱丽安·摩尔、连姆·尼森和阿曼达·塞弗里德共同主演了情色惊悚片《克洛伊》。2012年，他与詹妮弗·劳伦斯一起出演了恐怖片《街尽头的房子》。他目前在A&E的惊悚剧集《贝茨汽车旅馆》中扮演迪伦·马塞特。","name":"马克斯·塞奥特","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Макс Тириот","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"ماكس ثيريوت","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"マックス・シエリオット","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RS","iso_639_1":"sr","name":"Srpski","english_name":"Serbian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Макс Тириот","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Макс Тіріот","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"مکس تیریوت","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"맥스 시리엇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"מקס ת'יריוט","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"hi","name":"हिन्दी","english_name":"Hindi","data":{"biography":"","name":"मैक्स थेरियट","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GE","iso_639_1":"ka","name":"ქართული","english_name":"Georgian","data":{"biography":"","name":"მაქს ტირიოტი","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"馬克斯·泰瑞奥","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PL","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski","english_name":"Polish","data":{"biography":"Maximillion Drake Thieriot (ur. 14 października 1988) jest amerykańskim aktorem. Swoją karierę rozpoczął od ról w wielu filmach familijnych, w tym „Łapcie tę dziewczynę” z Kristen Stewart, „Pacyfikator” z Vinem Dieselem i „Nancy Drew” z Emmą Roberts. W 2009 roku zagrał w erotycznym thrillerze „Chloe” u boku Julianne Moore, Liama ​​Neesona i Amandy Seyfried. W 2012 roku zagrał w horrorze „Dom na końcu ulicy” u boku Jennifer Lawrence. Obecnie gra Dylana Massetta w dramatycznym thrillerze A&E „Bates Motel”.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TR","iso_639_1":"tr","name":"Türkçe","english_name":"Turkish","data":{"biography":"Maximillion Drake \"Max\" Thieriot, 14 Ekim 1988 tarihinde Los Altos Hills, Kaliforniya'da dünyaya gelmiştir. Çocukluğunu, ailesinin uzun yıllardır yaşadığı Occidental, Kaliforniya'da geçiren Thieriot, oyunculuk dünyasına tesadüfen adım attı. Bir doğaçlama dersinde yetenek avcısı bir menajer tarafından keşfedilmesiyle profesyonel oyunculuk kariyerinin temelleri atıldı.\n\nSinemaya ilk adımını 2004 yapımı macera filmi \"Catch That Kid\" ile attı. Ancak onu daha geniş kitlelere tanıtan rolü, 2005 yılında Vin Diesel ile başrolü paylaştığı başarılı aile komedisi \"Komando Dadı\" (The Pacifier) oldu. Bu filmdeki performansıyla Genç Sanatçı Ödülleri'ne aday gösterildi. Kariyerinin ilk yıllarında \"Nancy Drew\" (2007), \"Jumper\" (2008) ve eleştirmenlerce beğenilen \"Kit Kittredge: An American Girl\" (2008) gibi filmlerde rol alarak genç bir aktör olarak adını duyurmaya devam etti.\n\nGençlik filmlerinden sonra daha olgun ve farklı türlerdeki rollere yönelen Thieriot, usta yönetmen Wes Craven'in imzasını taşıyan korku filmi \"Hesaplaşma Günü\" (My Soul to Take) (2010) ve Jennifer Lawrence ile birlikte rol aldığı gerilim filmi \"Sokağın Sonundaki Ev\" (House at the End of the Street) (2012) gibi yapımlarda yer aldı.\n\nMax Thieriot'nun kariyerinde asıl büyük sıçrama televizyon dünyasında gerçekleşti. 2013-2017 yılları arasında yayınlanan ve büyük beğeni toplayan \"Psycho\" filminin öncesini anlatan \"Bates Motel\" dizisinde canlandırdığı Dylan Massett karakteriyle eleştirmenlerden tam not aldı. Dizi, onun bir karakter oyuncusu olarak ne kadar derinlikli olduğunu kanıtlamasını sağladı. \"Bates Motel\"in ardından, 2017'den 2022'ye kadar rol aldığı popüler askeri drama \"SEAL Team\"de Donanma Mührü Clay Spenser karakterini canlandırdı. Bu dizi sırasında sadece oyunculuk yapmakla kalmadı, aynı zamanda yönetmenlik koltuğuna da oturarak kariyerine yeni bir yön verdi.\n\nTelevizyondaki başarısını bir adım öteye taşıyan proje ise 2022'de başlayan \"Fire Country\" dizisi oldu. Thieriot, Kaliforniya'daki yangınlarla mücadele eden itfaiyecilerin hayatından esinlenerek yarattığı bu dizinin hem başrol oyuncusu (Bode Donovan karakteriyle) hem de yaratıcısı ve yönetici yapımcısıdır. Dizi, onun sadece bir oyuncu değil, aynı zamanda başarılı bir yapımcı ve hikaye anlatıcısı olduğunu da kanıtlayarak kariyerinin mevcut zirvesini oluşturmaktadır.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"（Maximillion Drake Thieriot，1988 年 10 月 14 日-），美國演員。他的職業生涯始於許多家庭電影，包括與克里斯汀·斯圖爾特合作的《抓住那個孩子》、與範·迪塞爾合作的《奶嘴》和與艾瑪·羅伯茨合作的《南希·德魯》。2009 年，他與朱麗安·摩爾、聯姆·尼森和阿曼達·塞弗里德共同主演了情色驚悚片《色破孽緣》。2012 年，他與詹妮弗·勞倫斯一起出演了恐怖片《街盡頭的房子》。他目前在 A&E 的驚悚劇集《貝茨汽車旅館》中扮演迪倫·馬塞特。","name":"麥斯·泰亞利奧特","primary":false}}]}},"person_1882418_translations":{"at":1773543127701,"data":{"id":1882418,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Voice actress from China. Representative works include the animation \"Soul Land\" and being the Chinese dub for the game \"Overwatch\" D.Va, \"League of Legends\" Rock Sparrow, \"Honkai 3\" Kiana Kaslana , \"Arknight\" Amiya. Lives in Shanghai now.","name":"Tao Dian","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"1992年10月5日出生。毕业于安徽师范大学传媒学院播音主持专业。\n\n2013年7月进入上海电影译制厂，目前在上海领声。\n\n2018年9月22日，参与配音的动画电影《大闹西游》在中国大陆上映。\n\n2019年7月13日，参与配音的网络动画《灵笼》播出。[5]8月9日，参与配音的游戏《最终王冠 X：新世界》开启全平台正式服。\n\n2022年7月17日，发行合唱单曲《无限的奇迹2022》。[7]9月10日，参加的综艺节目《我是特优声剧团季》定档在哔哩哔哩播出。\n\n配音代表作品：《精灵王座》《驯龙高手》TV版、《动物也疯狂》、《里约大冒险2》、《武庚纪》、《斗罗大陆》、《天行九歌》、《原神》、《崩坏3》《明日方舟》《无期迷途》 [34-35] [48] 等。陶典的配音自然清新，干净，甜美，被业界誉为\"最年轻的童音\"。","name":"陶典","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Dian Tao","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"1992 年 10 月 5 日出生。畢業於安徽師範大學傳媒學院播音主持專業。\n\n2013 年 7 月進入上海電影譯製廠，目前在上海領聲。\n\n2018 年 9 月 22 日，參與配音的動畫電影《大鬧西遊》在中國大陸上映。\n\n2019 年 7 月 13 日，參與配音的網絡動畫《靈籠》播出。8 月 9 日，參與配音的遊戲《最終王冠 X：新世界》開啟全平台正式服。\n\n2022 年 7 月 17 日，發行合唱單曲《無限的奇蹟 2022》。9 月 10 日，參加的綜藝節目《我是特優聲劇團季》定檔在嗶哩嗶哩播出。\n\n配音代表作品：《精靈王座》《馴龍記》TV 版、《動物也瘋狂》、《裏約大冒險 2》、《武庚紀》、《鬥羅大陸》、《天行九歌》、《原神》、《崩壞 3》《明日方舟》《無期迷途》 [34 - 35] 等。陶典的配音自然清新，乾淨，甜美，被業界譽為\"最年輕的童音\"。","name":"陶典","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Тао Дянь","primary":false}}]}},"person_4174215_translations":{"at":1773543128199,"data":{"id":4174215,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"陈玺月是中国内地的女性配音演员。毕业于浙江传媒学院。2019年，荣获中国西部动漫文化节首届配音大赛特等奖。2022年，加入瞬心文化。","name":"陈玺月","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Xiyue Chen","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Xiyue Chen","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"陳璽月是中國內地的女性配音演員。畢業於浙江傳媒學院。2019 年，榮獲中國西部動漫文化節首屆配音大賽特等獎。2022 年，加入瞬心文化。","name":"陳璽月","primary":false}}]}},"person_1010877_translations":{"at":1773599448078,"data":{"id":1010877,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.\n\nHan Ji-min (born November 5, 1982) is a South Korean actress. After minor roles in All In and Dae Jang Geum, Han had her breakout role in revenge series Resurrection in 2005. This was followed by period dramas Capital Scandal and Yi San, contemporary dramas Cain and Abel and Padam Padam, and romantic comedy Rooftop Prince.","name":"Han Ji-min","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"한지민","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韓志旼（韓語：한지민，1982年11月5日—），韓國女演員。\n\n代表作品： 電影: 《朝鮮名探長：烈女門秘辛》; 《逆鱗：刺王危城》; 《密探》; 《白小姐》; 電視劇: 《李算》; 《閣樓上的王子》; 《耀眼》; 《春夜》; 《我們的藍調時光》\n\n出道作品： 《All In 真愛賭注》","name":"韓志旼","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韩国女演员，毕业于首尔女子大学社会福利学系。2003年凭借《ALL IN》童年闵洙茵一角出道，同年凭借《大长今》信非一角被观众熟知。代表作有：电视剧《复活》《李算》《京城绯闻》《该隐与亚伯》《padam padam》，电影《朝鲜名侦探》《青燕》。","name":"韩志旼","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Han Ji Min é uma atriz sul-coreana popular. Nascida em 5 de novembro de 1982, ela começou sua carreira como modelo em comerciais e videoclipes enquanto ainda estava no ensino médio. Ela fez sua estreia como atriz nos dramas de televisão de 2003 \"All In\" e \"Dae Jang Geum\". Ela também apresentou o programa semanal de notícias do showbiz \"Entertainment Weekly\" de 2006 a 2008. Han Ji Min estrelou muitos filmes populares e dramas de televisão, incluindo \"Padam Padam\" (2011), \"Rooftop Prince\" (2012) e \"Hyde Jekyll, Me\" (2015), a primeira série dramática original da Viki \"Dramaworld\" (2016) e \"Familiar Wife\" (2018). Além de sua atuação, Han Ji Min é bem conhecida por seu trabalho voluntário. Em 2009, ela publicou um livro intitulado Já somos amigos: o livro de doações de Han Ji Min para as Filipinas, que continha desenhos e histórias de suas experiências como voluntária em uma escola em uma vila nas montanhas das Filipinas.","name":"Han Ji Min","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韓國女演員，畢業於首爾女子大學社會福利學系。2003 年憑借《ALL IN》童年閔洙茵一角出道，同年憑借《大長今》信非一角被觀眾熟知。代表作有：電視劇《復活》《李算》《京城緋聞》《該隱與亞伯》《padam padam》，電影《朝鮮名偵探》《青燕》。","name":"韓志旼","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ハン・ジミン","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"هان جی مین","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Han Ji-min","primary":false}}]}}}}